{"tid":1825956,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有班傻佬整咗個文宣庫俾大家搵文宣！","createTime":"2020-01-15T17:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T04:18:45.000Z","uid":267498,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d5bd55edd9f8e662e043e46e5718ff298cc6cc64","tid":1825956,"uid":267498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:44:07.000Z","msg":"呢半年文宣手足整咗咁多靚文宣！<br />\n如果以後搵唔返咪好浪費？<br />\n<br />\n我地整咗個以 Tag 去串連嘅文宣庫，將半年嚟嘅文宣收集好晒！但我地團隊人唔多，好難整理得晒呢半年嚟嘅文宣。所以我地整咗個 Game，等大家得閒嗰陣都可以一齊玩，欣賞下手足嘅文宣之餘，同時幫手 Tag 下啲文宣！<br />\n<br />\n版面簡單，方便大家隨時隨地用手機都玩到<br />\n&rarr; <a href=\"https://mylennonbuddy.com/game\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmylennonbuddy.com%2Fgame&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBmSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=f9e6b626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mylennonbuddy.com/game</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>遊戲玩法</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H429Tu3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH429Tu3.png&h=37bffb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始遊戲之後呢，你會見到一張相同兩條問題，喺第一條問題，點選<strong>關事</strong>嘅 Tag，然後喺第二條問題加返啲建議嘅 Tag，例如「米豬蓮」、「連豬」咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZsFfJr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZsFfJr.png&h=b5eb2c91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你見到張文宣咩 Tag 都冇，就記住幫手大大力 Tag 爆佢！好呢上面呢張咁，就可以幫手 Tag 返「11.30」、「中學生」、「銀髮族」、「遮打花園」、「人鏈」咁，同文宣內容相關嘅 Tag 啦！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">常見問題</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Tag 嚟做咩？</strong><br />\n<br />\nTag 完嘅相會出現喺 <a href=\"http://mylennonbuddy.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmylennonbuddy.com&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBmSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=57384144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">mylennonbuddy.com</a> ，咁想用嘅時候，就可以輕輕鬆鬆用大家嘅 Tag 搵返相關嘅圖！手足想痴連儂牆場、搞展覽嘅時候可以搵返，媒體想報導嘅時候，都可以上嚟搵！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Host 喺邊？</strong><br />\n<br />\n秘密。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>點解要登入 Gmail？</strong><br />\n<br />\n登入 Gmail 係我地用嚟防止有人惡意玩 Game，亂咁 Tag 亂咁寫而加嘅功能。當我地發現有人搞事，我地就可以封咗佢個帳戶，同移除佢整出嚟嘅「假 Tag」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有冇高清原圖啊？</strong><br />\n<br />\n我地目前嘅圖源都係 Twitter/Facebook/IG/Telegram，所以唔一定係高清。我地遲下會開放俾人 upload 原圖，如果你有高清嘅版本，到時可以 upload 上嚟。呢個功能做好之後會再通知大家！ <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>團隊的話</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地之後會陸續加更多功能，暫時計劃中嘅有︰<br />\n<br />\n- 自動將重複嘅圖整合埋一齊<br />\n- 開放上載／下載原圖嘅功能<br />\n- 批量下載<br />\n- Like / Saved 圖<br />\n- 建立唔同文宣嘅關係︰系列、相關文宣<br />\n- 收錄埋其他類型嘅創作︰歌詞、MV、影片<br />\n- 仲有好多好多&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n但如果個網站冇人睇，冇人幫手 Tag 文宣，我地加幾多功能都冇用！希望大家可以 share 個 website 俾朋友，返工返學搭車食飯嘅時間，幫下手 Tag 下文宣，唔好浪費文宣手足嘅心血！<br />\n<br />\n想留意我地，可以 follow 埋我地 <a href=\"http://t.me/mylennonbuddy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmylennonbuddy&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBmSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=b5269505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/mylennonbuddy</a><br />\n就知我地幾時出新功能啦！"},{"pid":"233ef47fd541e5f6a4b68de5c66f21b5d968a20c","tid":1825956,"uid":28759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:47:47.000Z","msg":"文宣手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a8a9b5e08833e4c682eb13aa19303a1a87443a","tid":1825956,"uid":119834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04064a82db8e09728daf1923df509c5d551b8e7a","tid":1825956,"uid":302831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:51:45.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"8dc52690c1d5c425fbda06c7db5050a5d9859f6f","tid":1825956,"uid":267498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:55:06.000Z","msg":"希望多啲人睇到<br />\n多啲人幫手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每